Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,UNTIL WE MEET AGAIN IN KAMOGAWA! MADOKA &amp; LAN &amp; MUGINAMI {17:24ish}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,WE ARE THE SWEATS CLUB FOREVER MADOKA &amp; LAN &amp; MUGINAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come to see you, Yurikano...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like a word with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If words won't work, I'll let my fists do the talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my Kamogawa Dynamite Bomber, taught to me by my Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've trampled on Yurikano's feelings enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you two get it by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You both mean a lot to Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She hated seeing the two of you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you both did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You let her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Yurikano had to leave again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You hurt Lan and Muginami too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've failed as kings!
