Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what became of the Vox Core possessed by Le Garite?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're told it was destroyed during the subspace distortion that took place in the fleet ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, everyone knows that Dizelmine was plotting to attack De Metrio
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,using the Vox and Yurikano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you still proceed with the Intergalactic Conference as scheduled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But it appears Dizelmine will not be joining the conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After coming all this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just hope this doesn't turn into a trial {\i1}in absentia{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come here to mock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I resorted to using my enemy's sister as part of my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead, I was thrown off by her confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I have lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done moping yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you two get it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know all the complicated details{\i0} {\i1}of the Polyhedron problem,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but there's still time, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case, why not work together{\i0} {\i1}to find a solution?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think you're despicable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did that girl punch two kings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,she even lectured both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that for completely losing face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a pretty good punch too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell have we been doing this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about what you think of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But is what happened between us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,really worth shedding so much blood and so many tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I became king because this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to move forward together with you for the sake of the Polyhedron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you find it in yourself to forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we resolve our differences, my sister won't find peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here at the Kamogawa Municipal Auditorium,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the Polyhedron Intergalactic Conference is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As each of the various Polyhedron representatives arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa was in a festive mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but yesterday's accident aboard the Le Garite flagship,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in satellite orbit above Earth, has caused an uproar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,First, regarding to the Polyhedron problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that the incident will not take place for another millennium
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,has led our thinking astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I alone went astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As all of you gathered here are aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it was my decision alone to use the power of the Vox and to resort to force.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to use this opportunity to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a concrete plan to deal with the Polyhedron problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that right now, the best we can do is put our heads together
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to come up with a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, as a first step, King Dizelmine and I will join forces
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring our two nations, Le Garite and De Metrio, together
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to reaffirm and renew friendly relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean the relationship between the two kings has been resolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So they've declared a ceasefire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A Success example of friendship cemented by quarrels,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the girls won't have to go out on missions anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It does seem that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a start, King Dizelmine{\i0} {\i1}stated that henceforth,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Le Garite would not use the Vox to solve{\i0} {\i1}the Polyhedron 1000-year Problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could've predicted that the Intergalactic Conference
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,would take such an exciting turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. This calls for a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Tadokoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:08:00.91,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(524,708)}So, what became of the Vox Core possessed by Le Garite?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}20,000 years ago,{\i0} {\i1}the people who fled Earth{\i0} {\i1}were scattered throughout{\i0} {\i1}the Universe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Today, through a strange twist of fate,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}their descendants have returned{\i0} {\i1}to this planet and become one again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}their descendants have returned{\i0} {\i1}to this planet and become one again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean it's finally over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess it is..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's hope it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a mountain of problems ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much we'll be able to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but all we can do is try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys buried the hatchet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come all this way just to tell us that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to get punched like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:08:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Succ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of asking me, you should just tell her yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done a lot of things to you, without thinking about your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a great opportunity to learn from this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the best of it by enjoying it as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All I ask is that you earn outstanding grades befitting a royal family member.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made fine friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back to calling me that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Miss Yurikano is your real sister, and I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop thinking about silly things and just do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be your big brother until the day I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These are images of the Vox deployment that took place the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you determined why the Vox launched without their pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything for sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's conceivable that they launched in response to Miss Kyono, thinking she was in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the Chairman's permission to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you have a number of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially in regards to Princess Yurikano...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's start with what just happened to the Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, they responded to her thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was more a result of their training.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The sympathetic resonance between Aura, Lympha and Ignis has increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring up the actual numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it appears as though they are reflecting the girls' relationship with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like you all to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's the Chairman?
