Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand math at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really get any more basic than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was behind in my studies, so I expected you to help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All this brainwork makes my brain feel like it's going to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But we just took one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Baked sweet potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good call, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Those three reek of depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's not contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because of how Lady Yurikano disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've have hit them pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are those three so committed to Yurikano?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of them were together
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,during their time at the Academy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they were in love with Yurikano?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Have either of you ever been in love before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What? Why do you ask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Muginami, why're you so flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not flustered....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See, back there, I was able to feel Yurikano's emotions very clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,About how much she cared about Lan's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you know what love feels like, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're growing up, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I know that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a bit different than loving baked sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did Yurikano tell Lan's brother that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,she thought he was despicable at the very end?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how your brother felt when she told him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother isn't one to show his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I sort of feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you put feelings that you've kept inside you into words,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,those feelings disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can understand why he doesn't want to put his feelings into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it better to come right out and say that you love a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If they share those feelings for each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All this is pretty grown-up stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fallen behind in this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have this, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop making fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've experienced one or two loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And another something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes three total.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized one more thing that day, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In her heart, Yurikano cares deeply not just for Lan's brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but for Big Brother Giuvi, Izo, Kirius, Array,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and for all of us, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's our turn to answer Yurikano's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you two come with me for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It always feels great up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,what're you looking for?
