Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that we will meet again in{\i0} {\i1}Kamogawa some day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You too, Lan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right. I vow too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as this lock remains here,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we must honor our vow,{\i0} {\i1}no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we made good on our vow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And so!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the three of us here again because I thought we could make a new vow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A new vow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we vow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking we should vow never to go to battle using the Vox again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two made up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There shouldn't be any more reasons to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Madoka Kyono, vow on this lock:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that I will never use Midori as a weapon, ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I vow that neither Hupo nor I will ever fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I vow here to use Orca for peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we make good on our vow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not graduate from the Jersey Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound so gung-ho, Madoka, but with your low grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't there a chance you might not graduate at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How can you say that?!
