Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something we've discovered recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're currently deciphering its origin and the meaning of these ancient characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He insisted on seeing it with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought a gift for you: milk buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take a look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue with the analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what's written on that stone tablet, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a... record of my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, the Rinne has caused two tragedies in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One is the Tragedy of Militia Zodia, brought about by Yurikano,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,when she attempted to seal away her powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The other happened 20,000 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,when the Earth was nearly destroyed when the Rinne blossomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who caused that tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,was Queen Maycun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jersey Club members!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind helping us out after school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Consider it done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Our club is back to three members again, so ask away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to the Jersey Club! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:07.01,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Jaajibu damashii! Jaajibu damashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:07.01,EDeng,,0,0,0,,The Jersey Club spirit! The Jersey Club spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:11.80,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Jaajibu damashii! Jaajibu damashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:11.80,EDeng,,0,0,0,,The Jersey Club spirit! The Jersey Club spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.56,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Jaajibu damashii! Jaajibu damashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.56,EDeng,,0,0,0,,The Jersey Club spirit! The Jersey Club spirit!
