Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:23.77,EDeng,,0,0,0,,Who cares what's correct right now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.77,0:22:25.65,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Mazu tonikaku koudou 
