Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:28.27,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Me no mae ni nayami ooki seishun 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:28.27,EDeng,,0,0,0,,Here in front of me is someone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:30.98,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Kakaeru kimi o mitsuketa yo isshun 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:30.98,EDeng,,0,0,0,,who carries around a billion issues
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:33.36,EDrom,,0,0,0,,damatte misugosenai shuusei 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:33.36,EDeng,,0,0,0,,I won't just shut up and leave you be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:36.91,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Utsumuki kagen senaka kyousei hora 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:36.91,EDeng,,0,0,0,,Lie down a while and you're fine again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:39.99,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Tonikaku sesuji o nobashitemite 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:39.99,EDeng,,0,0,0,,Let's just stretch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:41.24,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Tsukareteru ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:41.24,EDeng,,0,0,0,,I'm tired
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:42.62,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Hai! Kamogawa enajii!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:42.62,EDeng,,0,0,0,,Here, have some Kamogawa Energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:43.96,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Daijoubu! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:43.96,EDeng,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:46.33,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Zenbu nonda tte ii yo 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:46.33,EDeng,,0,0,0,,It's good to drink it all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:48.84,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Nihon nonda tte ii yo 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:48.84,EDeng,,0,0,0,,It's good to drink two
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:51.63,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Atashi no bun nante ki ni shinaide "e?" 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:51.63,EDeng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry how much I drink
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:55.26,EDrom,,0,0,0,,nande soko made shitekureru no tte? 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:55.26,EDeng,,0,0,0,,You ask me why I do so much for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:57.39,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Kimatteru jan sonna no 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:57.39,EDeng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:59.72,EDrom,,0,0,0,,"Kimi no yume ga mabushii kara!" 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:59.72,EDeng,,0,0,0,,I do it because your dreams are wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:04.65,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Jaajibu damashii! Jaajibu damashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:04.65,EDeng,,0,0,0,,The Jersey Club spirit! The Jersey Club spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:09.40,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Jaajibu damashii! Jaajibu damashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:09.40,EDeng,,0,0,0,,The Jersey Club spirit! The Jersey Club spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:14.12,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Jaajibu damashii! Jaajibu damashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:14.12,EDeng,,0,0,0,,The Jersey Club spirit! The Jersey Club spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:18.96,EDrom,,0,0,0,,Suketto shitai hadou hanatsu honki tamashii! 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:18.96,EDeng,,0,0,0,,I want to help you, hello and let's be cheery!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.24,0:23:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I was being watched just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be the girl who's been around since "Days"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Question! What do you mean by "Days"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It refers to "Kamogawa Days", also known as episode 12.5.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been watched for that long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how long she's been in the background.
